data.description: This home is located in a well established and desirable neighborhood in Lodi. 3 bedrooms 2 baths with an updated kitchen that includes beautiful new cabinets and well cared for hardwood floors. The backyard is your own oasis with fruit trees that include mandarin,lemon,avacado,fig,pear,plum,peach and orange all on a drip system.   This home has been lovingly maintained and is truly move in ready!
